{"tid":2399411,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"葵涌邨情侶爭執互毆　惹火水照頭淋縱火驚魂","createTime":"2021-02-08T06:22:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T15:23:05.000Z","uid":7452,"like":43,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"ec5f2d3e29decafb897cfca6216a881db19a44d8","tid":2399411,"uid":7452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T06:22:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NzdJiBU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNzdJiBU.png&h=fd49eb90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n葵涌邨碧葵樓一單位，今日(8日)凌晨2時許，一對情侶疑因「緣分已盡」爭執，且愈吵愈烈。現場消息稱，有人報警指遭人用易燃液照頭淋企圖放火。警方接報大為緊張，其後與消防趕至現場，證實無人淋潑易燃液體，事件中亦未有引起火警；惟發現一名男子手部受傷，其女友情緒激動哭泣，調查後列「襲擊致造成實際身體傷害」處理，並將該對涉案情侶拘捕及送院治理，其中涉案女子送院時仍激動哭泣。<br />\n此外，警員於現場發現一個相信盛載易燃液的空樽，亦檢走助查。"},{"pid":"545171f67d2fa5b5c4f3f47585470105e67617ec","tid":2399411,"uid":337986,"like":42,"dislike":36,"score":6,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T06:23:04.000Z","msg":"同公屋仔拍拖預咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68457962dfe888ea02eda0d4d28787302b466d3a","tid":2399411,"uid":7452,"like":89,"dislike":13,"score":76,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T06:24:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3dbe40bf4e790e1343401c0a455a44c7c75aa68a","tid":2399411,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T06:24:39.000Z","msg":"葵涌邨碧葵樓一單位"},{"pid":"ad37bd846f474e72d7d5f58bf6fbd2da74ca1a6e","tid":2399411,"uid":337986,"like":9,"dislike":7,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T06:26:07.000Z","msg":"好揀唔揀 同低下階層拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bda6e711c034b8f052e9627929784ac974111573","tid":2399411,"uid":7452,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"545171f67d2fa5b5c4f3f47585470105e67617ec","tid":2399411,"uid":337986,"like":42,"dislike":36,"score":6,"c